# Testing / verification rules

## Required test strategy
- parity/basic shape tests for new or corrected APIs
- positive runtime proof for `onChannelEvent(...)`
- updated Stage-6 parity/integration/canonical tests for operation-triggered branches
- section-tracking proof for any new generic workflow helper

## Primary oracle
- preprocess + official JSON + BlueId where structural comparison is appropriate
- runtime integration proof for behavioral claims

## Verification commands
- `npm install`
- `npx tsc -p libs/sdk-dsl/tsconfig.lib.json --noEmit`
- `npx tsc -p libs/sdk-dsl/tsconfig.spec.json --noEmit`
- `npx eslint libs/sdk-dsl`
- `npx vitest run --config libs/sdk-dsl/vite.config.ts`
- `npx vite build --config libs/sdk-dsl/vite.config.ts`
